---
// Hero for the homepage. Editorial layout matching /now and /about.
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-12 sm:pt-20 pb-16 sm:pb-24">
  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-orange-500 font-mono mb-6">
    Kundai Clayton Chatambudza · Digital garden
  </p>

  <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-[1.05]">
    Software for the<br />
    real world<span class="text-orange-500">.</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10">
    Full-stack mobile engineer building thoughtful, AI-assisted products. This is where the work lives alongside the thinking behind it — essays, notes, projects, half-formed ideas.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <a
      href="/about"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-orange-500 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors"
    >
      About me <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/garden"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 text-gray-300 text-sm font-medium hover:border-orange-500/40 hover:text-white transition-colors"
    >
      Explore the garden
    </a>
    <a
      href="/now"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 text-gray-300 text-sm font-medium hover:border-orange-500/40 hover:text-white transition-colors"
    >
      What I'm doing now
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
